title: Developer Attempts to Port Ubuntu Touch to the Sony Xperia Z Ultra Android Phone
text: Pedro Dias Vicente, a senior XDA member, posted news on the Ubuntu Touch mailing list informing developers and users alike about his attempt of porting Canonical's mobile operating system to the Sony Xperia Z Ultra smartphone.
